            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%83%BD%E5%85%BB%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%83%BD%E5%85%BB%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些方法能养胃#</span></a>？朋友们学起来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】胃不好饮食上要注意什么？专家提醒，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%BB%E8%83%83%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%88%AB%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%85%BB%E8%83%83%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%88%AB%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#养胃其实就是别伤胃#</span></a>，不伤就是养。避免天天吃辛辣食物，吃饭不要狼吞虎咽，而是尽量细嚼慢咽。日常生活中合理选择食物，避免一些不好的伤胃习惯，这就是在养胃。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%98%E7%9A%84%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%98%E7%9A%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃是怎样一步步癌变的#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6N5bTqP" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
